  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>QI</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sakura has asked Ryu to meet him at the school. She seems to have something important to tell him. A starry night and meeting between two friends. What challenge awaits Ryu !?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QI is a single one-boss-fight turn-based game made with RPG maker MV. Help Ryu defeat God for Sakura.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One-boss-battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat God</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Notes</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Around 80 min boss fight.</p>",
